  "response": "One music video that comes to mind is \"Thriller\" by Michael Jackson. Released in 1983, \"Thriller\" is one of the most iconic music videos of all time and revolutionized the music video industry with its elaborate production, choreography, and storyline. Directed by John Landis, it features Jackson's transformation into a werewolf and the famous zombie dance sequence. Learning more about the behind-the-scenes details, such as the creative decisions, special effects, choreography, and challenges faced during filming, would provide fascinating insights into the making of this legendary video.",
